s, or to activate defensive turrets. You will eventually die, but will you reach the top of the online scoreboard?\n<br><br><b>ESCAPE</b>: In this variation of Doomed mode, you can actually make it out alive! Battle through a series of increasingly difficult zones to reach the Exit in record time. Fight for the top spot on the online scoreboard.\n\n            \n    	566.79	1969-12-31	BR0	92	\N	\N	2021-12-19 23:19:46.019-03	2021-12-19 23:19:46.153-03
